node.text:
I decorated this set of floral cookies with the help of @eddie_edibleinkprinter! 

I created my own floral pattern on my tablet and then printed it directly onto my iced cookies. 

This printer is so much fun to use and I love that it allows me to be as creative as I want while saving me time. 

Watch the full video tutorial on my blog at SweetAmbs.com.

To learn more about Eddie, The Edible Ink Printer visit Primera.com/Eddie.
You can also join the Eddie user group on Facebook for tons of tips and tutorials!
 

#sweetambscookies #royalicingcookies #decoratedsugarcookies #edibleinkprinters #eddieedibleprinter
